  stimulus_text = 'The author’s main idea is that while the internet has the potential to be a powerful tool for connecting people, it is also a tool that can be used for malicious purposes. The author emphasizes this point by using a rhetorical question and then providing several examples of how the internet can be used to spread misinformation and hate speech. What rhetorical device does the author use to emphasize the point that the internet can be used for malicious purposes?',
